{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"✓ Quest 1 — Vote\n        \n        ✓ Quest 2 — Quiz\n        \n        ▶ Quest 3 — Debate\n        \n        🔒 Quest 4 — Follow\n      \n    \n    \n      A — Manual linear chain\n      Creator drags actions into an ordered list. Each quest unlocks the next. Most game-feel. Backend: new chain_index field on actions. Creator UI: a drag-arrange list. Clearest progression but adds creator setup burden and means the order is rigid.","choice":"manual","id":null,"timestamp":1775702652411}
